data.description: Welcome home ranch style with 3 bedrooms, plus office, 2 bathrooms &  nestled in the charming town of Ault. Lovely home boasts a multitude of appealing features that make it a standout choice. Inside starts with the open floor plan, then you'll find   a spacious kitchen with lots of cabinet space, walk-in pantry & island. The separate primary bedroom adds a touch of privacy as it's away from the additional bedrooms & features a 5 piece large primary bathroom with dual sinks, walk in shower & large bath tub. Additionally, water purifier included for your convenience. Outside, you'll appreciate fresh & newer exterior stucco that enhances curb appeal, the storage shed for keeping your belongings organized and out of the way. Corner lot with alley access with parking ensures you have plenty of space for vehicles & your toys. The large deck provides an excellent outdoor space for relaxation and gatherings. Notable updates include stucco that's just 3 years old, new carpet, and ceiling fans in every room, ensuring comfort throughout the home. This charming property is ready to become your next home. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and enjoy all the wonderful features it has to offer!
